        <section class="food-stalls">
            <div class="stall-card kathi">
                <h2>Kathi Roll Haven</h2>
                <p>At Kathi Roll Haven, we bring the streets of Kolkata to your plate. Our signature kathi rolls are a perfect blend of flaky paratha, succulent meats, and aromatic spices. Whether you're a vegetarian or a meat lover, we have a roll to satisfy your cravings. Don't miss our special "Fusion Rolls" that combine traditional Indian flavors with global influences. Each bite is a journey through the rich culinary heritage of India.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="stall-card maggie">
                <h2>Maggie Hotspot</h2>
                <p>Maggie Hotspot is your go-to place for quick, comforting meals. We've elevated the humble Maggi noodles to an art form, offering a variety of innovative flavors and toppings. From our spicy "Masala Blast" to the creamy "Cheese Explosion," each bowl is a nostalgic trip with a gourmet twist. Our secret recipes and fresh ingredients ensure that this isn't just any instant noodle – it's an experience.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="stall-card southern">
                <h2>Southern Stories</h2>
                <p>Southern Stories is where traditional South Indian cuisine meets modern presentation. Our dosas are crispy, our idlis are fluffy, and our sambhar is simply unforgettable. We take pride in sourcing authentic ingredients and using time-honored techniques to bring you the true flavors of South India. Don't forget to try our fusion dishes that blend Southern Indian tastes with international cuisines – our "Taco Dosa" is a crowd favorite!</p>
            </div>

            <div class="stall-card quench">
                <h2>Quench Station</h2>
                <p>Quench Station is your oasis of refreshment. We offer a wide range of beverages, from classic lassis and fresh fruit juices to innovative mocktails and bubble teas. Our drinks are not just thirst-quenchers; they're a celebration of flavors. Try our seasonal specials made with locally sourced fruits, or indulge in our decadent "Dessert Drinks" that double as a beverage and a treat. At Quench Station, we believe that great food deserves equally great drinks.</p>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section class="about-footer">
            <p>Each of our stalls is committed to quality, flavor, and a fantastic dining experience. We use fresh, locally-sourced ingredients wherever possible and prepare our food with love and care. Whether you're looking for a quick bite, a comforting meal, or a refreshing drink, our food stalls have something for everyone. Come, explore the diverse flavors at Bennett Foods!</p>
